	annotation = {EI: 是\\
	CCF: C\\
	TLDR: A thorough investigation of optimized convolutional neural networks developed for AMC using the three most commonly used model optimization techniques, showing that the proposed individual and combined optimization techniques are highly effective for developing models with significantly less complexity while maintaining or improving classification performance compared to the benchmark CNNs.},
